 .invoke delegates to this method upon any method invocation on the proxy instance, except Object.equals, Object.hashCode and Object.toString.

 {@inheritDoc}
  • {@code proxy.hashCode()} delegates to AbstractInvocationHandler.hashCode
  • {@code proxy.toString()} delegates to AbstractInvocationHandler.toString
  • {@code proxy.equals(argument)} returns true if:
    • {@code proxy} and {@code argument} are of the same type
    • and AbstractInvocationHandler.equals returns true for the InvocationHandler of {@code argument}
  • other method calls are dispatched to .handleInvocation.
